 Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo supplications have no barrier between them and Allah: the supplication of the oppressed, and the supplication of a man for his brother behind his back.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 11232 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11634,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/dua-oppressed-kafir\/","url_meta":{"origin":23205,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Fear supplications of oppressed, even unbelievers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of the supplication of the oppressed, even if he is an unbeliever, for there is nothing to block it.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 12549 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23208,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/14\/dua-oppressed-ascends-heaven\/","url_meta":{"origin":23205,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication of oppressed ascends to heaven","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of the supplication of the oppressed, for it ascends to the heavens as if it were a flare.\u201d Source: al-Mustadrak \u2018ala\u0301 al-S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323ayn 81 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5257,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/18\/three-dua-never-rejected\/","url_meta":{"origin":23205,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Three supplications always answered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree supplications are answered without a doubt: the supplication of an oppressed person, the supplication of a traveler, and the supplication of a parent over his child.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1905 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27524,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/dua-o